# =============================================================================
# Comprehensive .dockerignore Template
# =============================================================================
# This file excludes unnecessary files from the Docker build context.
# Benefits:
# - Faster builds (smaller context to send to Docker daemon)
# - Smaller images (no accidental inclusion of dev files)
# - Better security (no secrets copied into images)
#
# Usage:
#   Copy this file to your project root as ".dockerignore"
#   Uncomment sections relevant to your stack
#   Add project-specific exclusions as needed
# =============================================================================

